## Browser Automation

You have Playwright MCP tools (`browser_navigate`, `browser_snapshot`, `browser_click`,
`browser_type`, `browser_fill`, `browser_select_option`, `browser_screenshot`, `browser_wait`).
Use `browser_snapshot` to read page state (accessibility tree), act, then snapshot again to verify.
Browser profiles persist logins. Dismiss cookie popups automatically.
Confirm payments with the owner before clicking pay.
